-- France’s Sarkozy May Declare Candidacy on Feb. 15, Parisien Says
-- B y   R u d y   R u i t e n b e r g
-- 2012-02-11T11:54:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-11/france-s-sarkozy-may-declare-candidacy-on-feb-15-parisien-says.html
French President Nicolas Sarkozy may
declare his intention to run in this year’s presidential
elections on Feb. 15,  Le Parisien  reported, citing people close
to the president.  Sarkozy may announce his candidacy in a video message on
the evening news, the newspaper said. The timing of the
announcement is still open to change and may come a day later,
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rudy Ruitenberg in Paris at 
 rruitenberg@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  